DialogueNode.dialogue: Hey Stan, how are you today?
Oh hey... you... What was it again? Avery? Taylor?
Oh, yes. Of course. How silly of me.
Is that sarcasm? I hate sarcasm.
Hm. Direct. Honesty is an admirable quality.
Anyway, I should be getting back to work. See you later, Avery.
Anyway, I should be getting back to work. See you later, Alex.
